race.comment: SILVER WEDDING (3) is back from a 130-day spell. Opened last prep with an effortless win over this trip at Canterbury then went on to be competitive at Listed level in Brisbane just two runs later. Trialled well at this track on 3 October. McDonald hops off Waller's JELLICIOUS to ride this one which is significant. WRITTEN SCANDAL (8) couldn't go with them early then sprouted wings late to get up for third when resuming over 900m at Newcastle last time out. Both wins have come at today's journey so with that run under the belt she looks primed for a big performance. JELLICIOUS (4) was emphatic in taking out a similar race here three weeks ago at the second run of the prep. Goes up 3kgs but still has room to improve so keep her very safe. KIMBERLEY SECRETS (1) has been freshened up since failing in Saturday company on 6 September. This is a far more suitable assignment. CREPE MYRTLE (9) has switched to Joe Pride and is worth considering first-up.
